title: Good woman's eggs
ingredients: ['450g (1lb) potatoes, peeled and diced', 'Salt and black pepper', '1 teaspoon chopped rosemary', '3 tablespoons olive oil, plus extra for greasing', '1 large onion, finely sliced', '450g (1lb) butternut squash, peeled and diced', '3 large, flat mushrooms, roughly chopped', '2 cloves garlic, crushed', '3 slices of lean back bacon, roughly chopped', '6 small eggs', '1 tablespoon grated Parmesan cheese']
